&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Community nurses for our community nursing teams in the north east of Hampshire areas covering, Aldershot, Farnborough, Fleet and Yateley into their Dynamic, forward thinking team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We deliver complex care to people in their own homes and facilitate the best possible care ensuring people are provided with the care they require, where and when they require it.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We have a team of highly skilled community nurses as well as competent, supportive health care assistants and nursing associates. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you would like a new challenge in the Community and aspire to change how nursing is currently delivered, then this role may be for you.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Care driver essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Various shift patterns including weekends and night shifts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kelly Gray, 07557 926032&lt;/p&gt;
